低剂量率，脉冲式剂量率及高剂量率治疗的无病生存率和带病生存是相似的。<ref name="Lertsanguansinchai-2004" /><ref name="Hareyama-2002">{{cite journal|title=High-dose-rate versus low-dose-rate intracavitary therapy for carcinoma of the uterine cervix: a randomized trial|pages=117–124|issn=0008-543X|journal=Cancer|volume=94|issue=1|date=2002-01-01|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11815967|accessdate=2019-02-12|author=Masato Hareyama, Koh-ichi Sakata, Atushi Oouchi, Hisayasu Nagakura, Mitsuo Shido, Masanori Someya, Kazumitsu Koito|pmid=11815967|archive-date=2020-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200428053305/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11815967|dead-url=no}}</ref>
但是，高剂量率治疗的最大优势在于可以门诊形式进行治疗，<ref name="Viswanathan 2007" />治疗时间短， 为许多患者提供了便利。

