s|first3=Christophe|last4=Barillot|first4=Isabelle|last5=Truc|first5=Gilles|last6=d’Hombres|first6=Anne|last7=Maingon|first7=Philippe|access-date=2019-03-15|archive-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307074955/https://www.redjournal.org/article/S0360-3016%2899%2900377-6/abstract|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{Cite journal|title=High-dose-rate intraluminal brachytherapy (HDRIBT) for esophageal cancer|url=https://www.redjournal.org/article/0360-3016(91)90267-8/abstract|last=Miura|first=Takashi|last2=Kamikonya|first2=Norihiko|date=1991-10-01|journal=International Journal of Radiation Oncology • Biology • Physics|issue=5|doi=10.1016/0360-3016(91)90267-8|volume=21|pages=1133–1135|language=en|issn=0360-3016|pmid=1938510|last3=Taniguchi|first3=Midori|last4=Kurisu|first4=Kouichi|last5=Hishikawa|first5=Yoshio|access-date=2019-03-15|archive-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307074958/https://www.redjournal.org/article/0360-3016%2891%2990267-8/abstract|dead-url=no}}</ref>和緩和治療<ref name=":4">{{Cite journal|title=Brachytherapy for the palliation of dysphagia owing to esophageal cancer: A systematic review and meta-analysis of prospective studies|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.radonc.2016.12.034|last=Fuccio|first=Lorenzo|last2=Mandolesi|first2=Daniele|date=2017-03|journal=Radiotherapy and Oncology|issue=3|doi=10.1016/j.radonc.2016.12.034|volume=122|pages=332–339|issn=0167-8140|last3=Farioli|first3=Andrea|last4=Hassan|first4=Cesare|last5=Frazzoni|first5=Leonardo|last6=Guido|first6=Alessandra|last7=de Bortoli|first7=Nicola|last8=Cilla|first8=Savino|last9=Pierantoni|first9=Chiara}}</ref><ref name=":5">{{Cite journal|title=Single-dose brachytherapy versus metal stent placement for the palliation of dysphagia from oesophageal cancer: multicentre randomised trial|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/s0140-6736(04)17272-3|last=Homs|first=Marjolein YV|last2=Steyerberg|first2=Ewout W|date=2004-10|journal=The Lancet|issue=9444|doi=10.1016/s0140-6736(04)17272-3|volume=364|pages=1497–1504|issn=0140-6736|last3=Eijkenboom|first3=Wilhelmina MH|last4=Tilanus|first4=Hugo W|last5=Stalpers|first5=Lukas JA|last6=Bartelsman|first6=Joep FWM|last7=van Lanschot|first7=Jan JB|last8=Wijrdeman|first8=Harm K|last9=Mulder|first9=Chris JJ}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Palliation of advanced/recurrent esophageal carcinoma with high-dose-rate brachytherapy|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/s0360-3016(01)01822-3|last=Sharma|first=Vinay|last2=Mahantshetty|first2=Umesh|date=2002-02|journal=International Journal of Radiation Oncology*Biology*Physics|issue=2|doi=10.1016/s0360-3016(01)01822-3|volume=52|pages=310–315|issn=0360-3016|last3=Dinshaw|first3=Ketayun A|last4=Deshpande|first4=Raman|last5=Sharma|first5=Sanjay}}</ref>。治療性治療主要針對早期食道癌<ref name=":1" />，或是在接受體外照射放療後，對殘餘的腫瘤再進行近距離放射，可避免附近組織接受不必要的劑量<ref name=":2" /><ref name=":3" />。緩和性治療則可減緩食道狹窄而造成吞嚥困難、疼痛的問題，並能提升對局部復發的控制，可改善患者生存率<ref name=":4" /><ref name=":5" />。

食道癌近距离放疗過程，須採用適當的置放器或導管裝置，目前有加粗直徑的導管<ref name=":6">{{Cite journal|title=External beam radiation therapy with or without high-dose-rate intraluminal brachytherapy for patients with superficial esophageal carcinoma|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1002/(sici)1097-0142(19990715)86:2<220::aid-cncr5>3.0.co;2-o|last=Nishimura|first=Yasumasa|last2=Okuno|first2=Yoshishige|date=1999-07-15|journal=Cancer|issue=2|doi=10.1002/(sici)1097-0142(19990715)86:2<220::aid-cncr5>3.0.co;2-o|volume=86|pages=220–228|issn=0008-543X|last3=Ono|first3=Koji|last4=Mitsumori|first4=Michihide|last5=Nagata|first5=Yasushi|last6=Hiraoka|first6=Masahiro}}</ref><ref name=":1" /><ref name=":7">{{Cite journal|title=High-dose-rate brachytherapy for previously irradiated patients with recurrent esophageal cancer|url=http://link.springer.com/10.1007/s11604-007-0152-4|last=Nonoshita|first=Takeshi|last2=Sasaki|first2=Tomonari|date=2007-10-26|journal=Radiation Medicine|issue=8|doi=10.1007/s11604-007-0152-4|volume=25|pages=373–377|language=en|issn=0288-2043|last3=Hirata|first3=Hideki|last4=Toh|first4=Yasushi|last5=Shioyama|first5=Yoshiyuki|last6=Nakamura|first6=Katsumasa|last7=Honda|first7=Hiroshi}}</ref>或是於導管上新增一可膨脹裝置<ref name=":8">{{Cite journal|title=Optimum fractionation for high-dose-rate endoesophageal brachytherapy following external irradiation of early stage esophageal cancer|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/s0360-3016(98)00433-7|last=Akagi|first=Yukio|last2=Hirokawa|first2=Yutaka|date=1999-02|journal=International Journal of Radiation Oncology*Biology*Physics|issue=3|doi=10.1016/s0360-3016(98)00433-7|volume=43|pages=525–530|issn=0360-3016|last3=Kagemoto|first3=Masayuki|last4=Matsuura|first4=Kanji|last5=Ito|first5=Atsushi|last6=Fujita|first6=Kazushi|last7=Kenjo|first7=Masahiro|last8=Kiriu|first8=Hiroshi|last9=Ito|first9=Katsuhide}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Long-term results of definitive radiotherapy for stage I esophageal cancer|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.ijrobp.2004.12.042|last=Sai|first=Heitetsu|last2=Mitsumori|first2=Michihide|date=2005-08|journal=International Journal of Radiation Oncology*Biology*Physics|issue=5|doi=10.1016/j.ijrobp.2004.12.042|volume=62|pages=1339–1344|issn=0360-3016|last3=Araki|first3=Norio|last4=Mizowaki|first4=Takashi|last5=Nagata|first5=Yasushi|last6=Nishimura|first6=Yasumasa|last7=Hiraoka|first7=Masahiro}}</ref>，因食道組織富含肌肉，具有強烈的收縮能力，置放器或導管可有效擴張食道，使放射源在管腔內不會接觸到食道壁<ref name=":6" /><ref name=":7" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Curative radiotherapy with high-dose-rate brachytherapy boost for localized esophageal carcinoma: dose-effect relationship of brachytherapy with the balloon type applicator system|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/s0167-8140(99)00040-7|last=Yorozu|first=Atsunori|last2=Dokiya|first2=Takushi|date=1999-05|journal=Radiotherapy and Oncology|issue=2|doi=10.1016/s0167-8140(99)00040-7|volume=51|pages=133–139|issn=0167-8140|last3=Oki|first3=Yosuke|last4=Suzuki|first4=Takayuki}}</ref><ref name=":8" />。醫生在進行近距離治療時，會將置放器或導管放入患者食道部位，並用影像確定腫瘤位置，再連接後荷式治療機，將適當的計量傳送到治療區域。

近距離治療是一種有效的治療方式，治療時間短，降低副作用，造福許多食道癌患者。

