患者可能在治疗后短期内感到身体疲惫。<ref name="Macmillan-brachytherapy" /><ref name="Fieler-1997">{{cite journal|title=Side effects and quality of life in patients receiving high-dose rate brachytherapy|pages=545–553|issn=0190-535X|journal=Oncology Nursing Forum|volume=24|issue=3|date=1997-4|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9127366|accessdate=2019-02-12|author=V. K. Fieler|pmid=9127366|archive-date=2020-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200428053542/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9127366|dead-url=no}}</ref>

近距离治疗宫颈癌或前列腺癌可导致急性或暂时性尿路症状，如排尿困难、大小便失禁或排尿疼痛（尿痛）。<ref name="Frank-2007" /><ref name="Doust-2004">{{cite journal|title=A systematic review of brachytherapy. Is it an effective and safe treatment for localised prostate cancer?|pages=525–529|issn=0300-8495|journal=Australian Family Physician|volume=33|issue=7|date=2004-7|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/15301172|accessdate=2019-02-12|author=Jenny Doust, Emma Miller, Gillian Duchesne, Michael Kitchener, David Weller|pmid=15301172|archive-date=2020-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200428053546/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/15301172|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Magné-2009">{{cite journal|title=Patterns of care and outcome in elderly cervical cancer patients: a special focus on brachytherapy|pages=197–201|issn=1879-0887|journal=Radiotherapy and Oncology: Journal of the European Society for Therapeutic Radiology and Oncology|volume=91|issue=2|date=2009-5|doi=10.1016/j.radonc.2008.08.011|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/18954913|accessdate=2019-02-12|author=Nicolas Magné, Nathalie Casanova Mancy, Enrique Chajon, Pierre Duvillard, Patricia Pautier, Damienne Castaigne, Catherine Lhommé, Philippe Morice, Christine Haie-Meder|pmid=18954913|archive-date=2020-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200413092528/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/18954913|dead-url=no}}</ref>
也可能发生短暂性肠道运动增加、腹泻、便秘或直肠少量出血。<ref name="Frank-2007" /><ref name="Doust-2004" /><ref name="Magné-2009" />急性和次急性副作用通常在几天或几周内缓解。对于前列腺癌永久性粒子植入近距离治疗，也有少量病例，可能出现一些粒子从治疗区域转移到膀胱或尿道，通过尿液排出。

在治疗结束的几周内，近距离治疗皮肤癌可能会引起治疗区域周围皮肤表层脱落（脱离），这种情况通常可在5-8周内康复。<ref name="GEC-ESTRO-Skin" />如果癌症位于唇部，可能会引起溃疡，但通常4-6周后就可缓解。<ref name="Casino-2006">
